{{死刑}}
死刑在[[以色列|以色列]]是一种合法的刑罚。在这个国家的历史上，只判处过两次死刑，而且只对战争期间犯下的罪行，如[[种族灭绝罪|种族灭绝罪]]、[[反人类罪|反人类罪]]、[[战争罪|战争罪]]、反犹太人罪、[[叛国罪|叛国罪]]和某些军事法下的罪行判处死刑。

以色列继承了英国授权的[[巴勒斯坦托管地|巴勒斯坦]]法典，其中包括对几种罪行判处死刑，但在1954年，以色列废除了对谋杀犯的死刑。虽然死刑在法律上是一种合法判决，但以色列几乎不使用死刑。最后一次执行死刑是在1962年，当时大屠杀主犯[[阿道夫·艾希曼|阿道夫·艾希曼]]因种族灭绝和反人类罪被处以绞刑。以色列最后一次判处死刑是在1988年，当时[[约翰·德米扬鲁克|约翰·德米扬鲁克]]因战争罪和反人类罪被判处死刑，但是他的判决（和定罪）后来在1993年向[[以色列最高法院|以色列最高法院]]上诉后被推翻。自20世纪90年代以来，以色列检察官没有再要求法庭判处死刑。

== 历史 ==
以色列很少使用死刑，部分原因可能是[[犹太教|犹太教]]法的影响。<ref>Mishnah Makot 1:10</ref>圣经中的律法明确规定对36种犯罪判处死刑，从谋杀、[[通奸|通奸]]到[[偶像崇拜|偶像崇拜]]和[[亵渎|亵渎]]安息日。然而，在古代以色列，死刑很少执行。自[[公元元年|公元元年]]以后，犹太学者就制定了对死刑的诸多限制，以防止处决无辜者，因此死刑在实际上已被废除。[[摩西·迈蒙尼德|摩西·迈蒙尼德]]认为，如果没有绝对把握就处决被告，将导致证据变得越来越没有意义，直到我们仅仅“根据法官的反复无常”来定罪。他关心的是维护公众对法律的尊重，认为犯罪造成的恶果比不作为造成的恶果更具威胁性。<ref>Moses Maimonides, ''The Commandments, Neg. Comm. 290'', at 269–71 (Charles B. Chavel trans., 1967).</ref>保守的犹太宗教领袖和学者认为死刑不应该被废除，甚至可以通过政治暗杀这种极端的手段。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Conservative Responsa in Israel - Masorti Responsa - Schechter Institute of Jewish Studies - SIJS|url = http://www.responsafortoday.com/moment/4_1.htm|website = www.responsafortoday.com|access-date = 2015-07-16|archive-date = 2015-12-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151214122446/http://responsafortoday.com/moment/4_1.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>

当现代的[[以色列|以色列]]在1948年建立时，它继承了英国托管地的法律，只做了一些微调，因此保留死刑。第一次处决发生在以色列独立战争期间，当时以色列军官梅厄·托比安斯基被诬告从事间谍活动。他在军事法庭上被判有罪之后被[[行刑队|行刑队]]处决，但后被证明无罪。

1948年12月委员会决定如果再出现死刑判决，必须上报上诉法院，得到批准后才可以执行。以色列民事法院对两名被判犯有谋杀罪的阿拉伯人做出第一次死刑判决，于1949年11月得到上诉法院的确认，但由于[[哈伊姆·魏茨曼|哈伊姆·魏茨曼]]总统反对死刑，判决被减刑为[[终身监禁|终身监禁]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://jpress.org.il/Olive/APA/NLI_Heb/SharedView.Article.aspx?parm=WV643k%2FWpfocKmYPSyqWXo0VDhgU8zo7EYDqG1GSYrhW8E8UvLSAWiyCdmubomgEYw%3D%3D&mode=image&href=MAR%2f1961%2f02%2f17&page=23&rtl=true|title = מיתת־תליה" – חודש הסעיף שבוטל"|last = Shaul|first = Hon|date = 1961-02-17|access-date = 2015-07-16|trans-title = "Bed of hanging" – the clause which was cancelled was renewed|page = 23|newspaper = [[Maariv|Maariv]]|language = he|archive-date = 2020-10-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201024054602/http://jpress.org.il/Olive/APA/NLI_Heb/SharedView.Article.aspx?parm=WV643k%2FWpfocKmYPSyqWXo0VDhgU8zo7EYDqG1GSYrhW8E8UvLSAWiyCdmubomgEYw%3D%3D&mode=image&href=MAR%2F1961%2F02%2F17&page=23&rtl=true|dead-url = no}}</ref>1949年7月，以色列内阁首次考虑废除死刑。

1950年，以色列有7名杀人犯被判死刑。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-3339783,00.html|title=הנידונים למוות|first=ינון|last=רויכמן|date=2006-12-14|via=Ynet|access-date=2021-03-23|archive-date=2018-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180803165035/https://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-3339783,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>1951年，以色列内阁再次提议废除死刑。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.jta.org/1951/10/30/archive/abolition-of-death-penalty-in-israel-proposed-by-cabinet|title = Abolition of Death Penalty in Israel Proposed by Cabinet|date = 1951-10-30|newspaper = Jewish Telegraphic Agency|quote = The Israel Cabinet last night decided to submit to the Parliament a law proposing abolition of the death penalty.|accessdate = 2021-03-23|archive-date = 2018-08-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180803194131/https://www.jta.org/1951/10/30/archive/abolition-of-death-penalty-in-israel-proposed-by-cabinet|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.jta.org/1953/12/17/archive/israel-will-not-carry-out-death-sentences-immediately|title = Israel Will Not Carry out Death Sentences Immediately|date = 1953-12-17|access-date = 2015-07-16|newspaper = Jewish Telegraphic Agency|quote = The Israel Government has no intention of proceeding at this time with execution of death penalties, Minister of Justice Pinhas Rosen told Parliament’s legal committee tonight in a statement [...]|archive-date = 2018-08-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180803163752/https://www.jta.org/1953/12/17/archive/israel-will-not-carry-out-death-sentences-immediately|dead-url = no}}</ref>1950年的《纳粹和纳粹同伙惩罚法》对最严重的罪行规定了强制性的死刑判决。1952年，该法首次对耶切克尔·英格斯特判处死刑，罪行是虐待和殴打其他犹太人而涉嫌[[反人类罪|反人类罪]]。但是他失去了一条腿并且患有心脏病，法院建议对这次死刑判决予以减刑。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jta.org/1952/01/07/archive/first-israeli-sentenced-to-death-for-torturing-nazi-victims |date=1952-01-07 |title=First Israeli Sentenced to Death for Torturing Nazi Victims |newspaper=[[Jewish_Telegraphic_Agency|Jewish Telegraphic Agency]] |access-date=2020-04-28 |archive-date=2018-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180803163642/https://www.jta.org/1952/01/07/archive/first-israeli-sentenced-to-death-for-torturing-nazi-victims |dead-url=no }}</ref>英格斯特曾入狱服刑，后来被赦免，但在获释后不久就去世了。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/.premium-the-nazi-collaborator-who-served-ice-cream-in-tel-aviv-1.5379313 |title=The Nazi Collaborator Who Served Ice Cream in Tel Aviv |date=2015-12-20 |newspaper=Haaretz |access-date=2020-04-28 |archive-date=2020-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629155143/https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/.premium-the-nazi-collaborator-who-served-ice-cream-in-tel-aviv-1.5379313 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1953年，又一个谋杀犯被判处死刑，但并未执行。六年后，被定罪的凶手获得了总统特赦。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://jpress.org.il/Olive/APA/NLI_Heb/SharedView.Article.aspx?parm=%2FHJYmaMuW0OIYAMoUfYvr1dueMAxRq0Av0moSTf8LamRy%2BJ51%2BsE8B6dX2atP8pwYw%3D%3D&mode=image&href=MAR%2f1959%2f03%2f18&page=2&rtl=true |date=1959-03-18 |access-date=2020-04-28 |title=הנ ידון למוות - שוחרר מהכלא - מעריב, 18/03/1959 |language=he |trans-title=Sentenced to death - released from prison - Maariv, 18/03/1959 |newspaper=[[Maariv_(newspaper)|Maariv]] |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024023105/http://jpress.org.il/Olive/APA/NLI_Heb/SharedView.Article.aspx?parm=%2FHJYmaMuW0OIYAMoUfYvr1dueMAxRq0Av0moSTf8LamRy+J51+sE8B6dX2atP8pwYw%3D%3D&mode=image&href=MAR%2F1959%2F03%2F18&page=2&rtl=true |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1954年，议会投票废除对谋杀罪的死刑。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.jta.org/1954/02/17/archive/israel-parliament-votes-to-abolish-capital-punishment|title = Israel Parliament Votes to Abolish Capital Punishment|date = 1954-02-17|access-date = 2015-07-16|newspaper = Jewish Telegraphic Agency|quote = The Israel Parliament today abolished the death penalty for the crime of murder. The vote was 61 to 33, with two abstentions.|archive-date = 2020-08-31|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200831162915/https://www.jta.org/1954/02/17/archive/israel-parliament-votes-to-abolish-capital-punishment|dead-url = no}}</ref>对战争罪、危害人类罪、危害犹太人民罪、叛国罪和战时军事法规定的某些罪行保留死刑。

1962年，第二次处决，也是唯一一次民事处决发生在[[阿道夫·艾希曼|阿道夫·艾希曼]]在1961年被判犯有与大屠杀有关的纳粹战争罪后被处以绞刑的时候。

在接下来的几十年里，被判犯有恐怖主义罪行的人偶尔会被判处死刑，但这些判决总是会被减刑。1988年，战争期间纳粹死亡集中营的警卫[[约翰·德米扬鲁克|约翰·德米扬鲁克]]被囚犯们戏称为“恐怖伊万”，因犯有[[战争罪|战争罪]]被判死刑，但后来上诉时判决被推翻。20世纪90年代中期，要求对面临恐怖主义指控的人判处死刑的做法停止了。<ref name=haaretz>{{cite web|url=http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/news/idf-expected-to-seek-death-penalty-for-killers-of-fogel-family-1.362893|title=IDF Expected to Seek Death Penalty for Killers of Fogel Family|first=Chaim|last=Levinson|date=2011-05-20|via=Haaretz|access-date=2021-03-23|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924222718/http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/news/idf-expected-to-seek-death-penalty-for-killers-of-fogel-family-1.362893|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2011年伊塔马尔袭击事件之后，死刑问题再次短暂地出现。预计以色列军事检察官将寻求对肇事者判处死刑，<ref name=haaretz/>但最终没有这样做。尽管如此，法官在决定对其中一名罪犯的判决时认真考虑过判处死刑，但最终决定不判处死刑，因为检方没有提出要求。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/national/idf-court-gives-palestinian-five-life-sentences-for-itamar-murders-1.407626 |title=IDF court gives Palestinian five life sentences for Itamar murders |access-date=2021-03-23 |archive-date=2019-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512071536/https://www.haaretz.com/1.5166094 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2015年3月的选举中，[[以色列是我们的家园|以色列是我们的家园]]的竞选纲领包括对恐怖分子判处死刑。同年7月，一名该党成员提出了一项法案，允许多数主审法官判处一名恐怖分子死刑。该法案在一读时以94-6票被否决。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Knesset votes down death penalty for terrorists 94-6|url = http://www.jpost.com/Israel-News/Politics-And-Diplomacy/Knesset-votes-down-death-penalty-for-terrorists-94-6-409077|website = The Jerusalem Post|access-date = 2015-07-16|archive-date = 2020-10-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201014012336/https://www.jpost.com/israel-news/politics-and-diplomacy/knesset-votes-down-death-penalty-for-terrorists-94-6-409077|dead-url = no}}</ref>
=== 要求判处死刑 ===
以色列政界人士有时呼吁对特定罪犯判处死刑。2010年，议会成员阿尤布·卡拉呼吁对塔普亚交叉路口持刀行凶者判处死刑。<ref name="MurderedAtJunction">{{cite news|title=Shomron Honors Druze Soldier Murdered at Tapuach Junction|url=http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/142472|access-date=2017-07-24|publisher=Israel National News|date=2011-02-22|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024023231/http://www.israelnationalnews.com/News/News.aspx/142472|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年，包括总理[[本雅明·内塔尼亚胡|本雅明·内塔尼亚胡]]在内的政治人物呼吁对2017年哈拉米什持刀袭击案的行凶者判处死刑。<ref name="DeathPenaltyHalamish">{{cite news|title=Netanyahu demands death penalty for Halamish terrorist|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/netanyahu-demands-death-penalty-for-halamish-terrorist/|access-date=2017-07-27|work=Times of Israel|date=2017-07-27|archive-date=2020-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006120138/https://www.timesofisrael.com/netanyahu-demands-death-penalty-for-halamish-terrorist/|dead-url=no}}</ref>政府的代表计划向议会提出一项法案，允许对恐怖份子判处死刑。<ref>{{cite news |author1=AKTUALISIERT |title=Israel will Todesstrafe für Terroristen einführen |url=https://www.faz.net/aktuell/politik/ausland/israel-will-todesstrafe-fuer-terroristen-einfuehren-15347505.html |accessdate=2017-12-17 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024023317/https://www.faz.net/aktuell/politik/ausland/israel-will-todesstrafe-fuer-terroristen-einfuehren-15347505.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2018年1月，以色列议会以52票对49票的初步投票通过了一项法案，该法案使军事法庭更容易宣判死刑。内塔尼亚胡投了赞成票，但后来表示，该法案需要部长们进行“更深入的讨论”，才能再次投票表决。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Reuters Staff |title=Israeli death penalty advocates win preliminary vote in parliament |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-israel-palestinians-deathpenalty/israeli-death-penalty-advocates-win-preliminary-vote-in-parliament-idUSKBN1ES1DT |accessdate=2018-01-04 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808073336/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-israel-palestinians-deathpenalty/israeli-death-penalty-advocates-win-preliminary-vote-in-parliament-idUSKBN1ES1DT |dead-url=no }}</ref>内塔尼亚胡表示，他将支持一项将死刑作为普遍惩罚的法案。<ref>[https://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/opinion/ways-israel-sentence-palestinians-death-181217105304720.html Israel is now considering to bring back capital punishment to deal with the resistance.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/opinion/ways-israel-sentence-palestinians-death-181217105304720.html |date=20200720004059 }} from : aljazeera.com</ref>如果拟议的法案成为法律，它将允许[[约旦河西岸|约旦河西岸]]（包括[[东耶路撒冷|东耶路撒冷]]）的[[以色列国防军|以色列国防军]]军事法庭对那些被判犯有恐怖主义罪的人判处死刑，但必须得到一个法官小组的多数同意。

[[阿维格多·利伯曼|阿维格多·利伯曼]]和他的[[以色列是我们的家园|以色列是我们的家园党]]强烈支持对恐怖分子判处死刑。<ref>{{Cite web|title=ליברמן: “נגיש חוק עונש מוות למחבלים"|url=https://beytenu.org.il/ליברמן-נגיש-חוק-עונש-מוות-למחבלים/|date=2015-02-17|website=ישראל ביתנו|language=he-IL|access-date=2020-05-30|archive-date=2019-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190621082603/https://beytenu.org.il/%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%91%D7%A8%D7%9E%D7%9F-%D7%A0%D7%92%D7%99%D7%A9-%D7%97%D7%95%D7%A7-%D7%A2%D7%95%D7%A0%D7%A9-%D7%9E%D7%95%D7%95%D7%AA-%D7%9C%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%91%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9D/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Liberman: We will not give up until death penalty bill is approved|url=https://www.jpost.com/breaking-news/liberman-we-will-not-give-up-until-death-penalty-bill-is-approved-571161|access-date=2020-11-18|website=The Jerusalem Post {{!}} JPost.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226104153/https://www.jpost.com//Breaking-News/Liberman-We-will-not-give-up-until-death-penalty-bill-is-approved-571161|dead-url=no}}</ref>
